name: Fire/flare girls (element) by YeiyeiArt
description:
“This model is a proof of a concept that suddenly occurred to me and I thought it could be interesting. Basically it transforms your characters into fire in a more exaggerated way, unlike using only prompts. The model is mostly trained with images of girls, so it will be easier to create fire girls.

It has not been tested on objects but I think it could work. I recommend using Lora with forces from (1.0 - 0.4).

The larger the weight of the Lora, the model will acquire a stone or limestone armor, that’s what I’ve been able to observe while testing it. If you want a more flaming and clean body, reduce the Lora to (0.4). To invoke the Lora I recommend using the following keywords (FireFull) and also works (girl by FireFull) for greater precision. Additionally use the following keywords to get a better flaming body (fire skin, yellow skin:2).”

CHECK THE OTHER LORAS!!!
